title: Damaged Oroville Dam spillway undergoes more water releases
text: Damaged Oroville Dam spillway undergoes more water releases Feb 09, 2017 Water continues to be released along the damaged Oroville Dam spillway on Thursday, February 9, 2017. Eric See of says the Department of Water Resources will monitor and assess the spill.
